question: Taun pira sing nuduhake owah-owahan paling gedhe ing 'Net interest income excluding cib markets' saka taun sadurunge?
Pira rata-rata 'average interest-earning assets' ing telung taun sing diwenehake?
Nalika 'cib markets net interest income' paling dhuwur, pinten rega 'average cib markets interest-earning assets'?
Jelasno tren 'net interest yield on average cib markets interest-earning assets' teko 2015 nganti 2017.
answer: Tren-ne iku jiga bolak-balik. Tingkat bunga mundhak kira-kira 17,3% teko 1,04 nang taun 2015 dadi 1,22 nang taun 2016, tapi terus mudhun drastis kira-kira 29,5%, dadi 0,86 nang taun 2017.

question: Sebutna taun-taun ing ngendi 'cib markets net interest income' luwih saka $5.000 yuta lan 'net interest yield on average cib markets interest-earning assets' luwih saka 1.10.
Nang taun 2016, pira persene 'rata-rata aset penghasil bunga pasar cib' saka 'rata-rata aset penghasil bunga'?
Nek 'cib markets net interest income' ing taun 2017 mundhak 20% nanging 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' tetep padha, pira 'net interest income excluding cib markets' sing anyar?
Miturut tabel, apa ana gegayutan sing katon antarane 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' sakabèhé lan 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets 2013 managed basis' ing telung taun?
answer: Ya, ana gegayutan positif sing cetha. Nalika 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' terus mundhak saka $44.620 yuta ing 2015 dadi $51.410 yuta ing 2017, 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets 2013 managed basis' uga nuduhake kenaikan terus-terusan saka 2,14% dadi 2,36% sajrone wektu sing padha.

question: Metrik opo loro neng tabel iki, nek sing siji dibagi karo sing nomer loro, iso ngitung 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets excluding cib markets'?
answer: net interest income excluding cib markets ( a )
average interest-earning assets excluding cib markets

question: Taun pira 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' sing dadi outlier nek dibandingke karo thone liyane babagan pertumbuhane saben taun?
answer: 2017 dadi outlier amarga pertumbuhane luwih dhuwur. Peningkatan saka 2016 nganti 2017 yaiku $4.118 yuta ($51.410 - $47.292), sing luwih gedhe tinimbang peningkatan $2.672 yuta saka 2015 nganti 2016 ($47.292 - $44.620).
